<body>
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h1 class="text-center mb-4">About Us</h1>

        <div class="card shadow-sm about-us">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h2 class="card-title">Welcome to Best Burger!</h2>
                <p class="card-text">
                    At Best Burger, we are passionate about crafting the perfect burger. Established in 2010, our mission is to bring you the highest quality, most delicious burgers you’ve ever tasted. Located in the heart of the city, our restaurant offers a vibrant and welcoming atmosphere where you can enjoy a meal with family and friends.
                </p>
                <p class="card-text">
                    Our journey began with a simple idea: to create a place where burgers are more than just a meal—they’re an experience. We use only the freshest ingredients, sourced from local farms, to ensure that every bite of our burgers is flavorful and satisfying. Our team of skilled chefs is dedicated to perfecting every recipe and delivering a dining experience that will keep you coming back for more.
                </p>
                <p class="card-text">
                    At Best Burger, we believe in supporting our community. That’s why we partner with local businesses and farms to bring you the best ingredients while contributing to the local economy. Our commitment to sustainability and quality is evident in everything we do, from our eco-friendly packaging to our farm-to-table approach.
                </p>
                <p class="card-text">
                    We are more than just a burger place—we’re a community hub. Whether you’re stopping by for a quick lunch, celebrating a special occasion, or just catching up with friends over a burger and fries, we strive to make every visit memorable. Our friendly staff is always here to ensure that you have a great time and enjoy the best burger experience possible.
                </p>
                <p class="card-text">
                    Thank you for choosing Best Burger. We look forward to serving you and becoming a part of your favorite dining experiences. If you have any questions or feedback, don’t hesitate to reach out. Your satisfaction is our top priority, and we are always eager to hear from our valued customers.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
